<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="J%20Biomed%20Inform"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Implementations of the HL7 Context-Aware Knowledge Retrieval (“Infobutton”) Standard: Challenges, Strengths, Limitations, and Uptake</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Del%20Fiol%20G"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Guilherme Del Fiol</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Guilherme Del Fiol</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Biomedical Informatics Department, University of Utah, Salt Lake City, UT, USA
</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Del%20Fiol%20G"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Guilherme Del Fiol</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Huser%20V"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Vojtech Huser</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Vojtech Huser</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Clinical Center, National Institutes of Health, Bethesda, MD, USA
</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Huser%20V"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Vojtech Huser</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Strasberg%20HR"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Howard R Strasberg</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Howard R Strasberg</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, MS</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>Wolters Kluwer Health, San Diego, CA, USA
</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Strasberg%20HR"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Howard R Strasberg</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>3</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Maviglia%20SM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Saverio M Maviglia</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Saverio M Maviglia</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, MSc</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Partners Healthcare, Wellesley, MA, USA
</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Maviglia%20SM"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Saverio M Maviglia</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>4</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Curtis%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Clayton Curtis</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Clayton Curtis</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>5</sup>Department of Veterans Affairs, Boston, MA, USA
</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Curtis%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Clayton Curtis</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>5</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Cimino%20JJ"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id6"><span class="name western">James J Cimino</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id6">
<h3>
<span class="name western">James J Cimino</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Clinical Center, National Institutes of Health, Bethesda, MD, USA
</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Cimino%20JJ"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">James J Cimino</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="anp_a" aria-expanded="false">Article notes</button></li>
